S.FORM: Elmer Behnke ( NBA ) Elmer Behnke ( NBA ) Elmer Behnke nalecuh i Rockford, Illinois, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. Elmer Behnke i 1951 a mihcaan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 4 ku uwac atu silsil 37, namapili' tu nu Rochester Royals putiput. nalecuhan ciniza i 2 bulad 3 demiad, 1929 a mihcaan, Elmer Behnke, u miunduay ciniza. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players wikipayke NBA
